data.description: Perfect for a large or growing family This great home in Northwest Laurens County has it all! FIVE (5) bedrooms and 3.5 bath; a separate office that could be a 6th bedroom if needed. Large kitchen with breakfast area, formal dining room, and living area with fireplace. The master suite is downstairs with spacious walk-in closet, and master bath with separate tub and shower. Brand new carpet downstairs and fresh paint.Tons of storage! Outside, enjoy the great back deck overlooking the salt water in-ground pool and the 3.13 acres ,perfect for outdoor activities.
